== Licensing: ==
{{ShouldBeSVG|diagram}}
{{PD-self}}

{{Ada/Navigation|80}}
__TOC__

'''Ada&nbsp;80''' was a preliminary version of the Ada programming language. The Military Standard reference manual was approved on December 10, 1980 ([[Wikipedia:Ada Lovelace|Ada Lovelace]]'s birthday), and given the number '''MIL-STD-1815''' in honor of Ada Lovelace's birth year.

The [[Ada Programming/Ada 83|Ada&nbsp;83]] standard, MIL-STD-1815''A'', was later derived from Ada&nbsp;80.

Ada&nbsp;80 is just interesting from a historic point of view, there is no code that must conform with this standard.

== Summary of features ==

=== Pragmas ===

* {{Ada/pragma|Controlled}} 
* {{Ada/pragma|Include}} (not in Ada&nbsp;83)
* {{Ada/pragma|Inline}}
* {{Ada/pragma|Interface}}
* {{Ada/pragma|List}}
* {{Ada/pragma|Memory_Size}}
* {{Ada/pragma|Optimize}}
* {{Ada/pragma|Pack}}
* {{Ada/pragma|Priority}}
* {{Ada/pragma|Storage_Unit}}
* {{Ada/pragma|Suppress}}
* {{Ada/pragma|System_Name}} (named {{Ada/pragma name|System}} in Ada&nbsp;83)

The following pragmas were not defined in Ada&nbsp;80, but were later added in Ada&nbsp;83:
* {{Ada/pragma|Elaborate}} (Ada&nbsp;83 only)
* {{Ada/pragma|Page}} (Ada&nbsp;83 only)
* {{Ada/pragma|Shared}} (Ada&nbsp;83 only)

=== Attributes ===

<div style="-moz-column-count:4; column-count:4;">
* {{Ada/attribute|Actual_Delta}} (not in Ada&nbsp;83)
* {{Ada/attribute|Address}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Base}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Bits}} (not in Ada&nbsp;83)
* {{Ada/attribute|Constrained}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Count}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Delta}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Digits}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Emax}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Epsilon}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Failure}} (not in Ada&nbsp;83)
* {{Ada/attribute|First}}
* {{Ada/attribute|First_Bit}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Image}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Large}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Last}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Last_Bit}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Length}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Machine_Emax}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Machine_Emin}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Machine_Mantissa}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Machine_Overflows}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Machine_Radix}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Machine_Rounds}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Mantissa}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Pos}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Position}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Pred}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Priority}} (not in Ada&nbsp;83)
* {{Ada/attribute|Range}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Size}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Small}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Storage_Size}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Succ}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Terminated}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Val}}
* {{Ada/attribute|Value}}
</div>

The following attributes were later added to Ada&nbsp;83:
* {{Ada/attribute|Aft}} (Ada&nbsp;83 only)
* {{Ada/attribute|Callable}} (Ada&nbsp;83 only)
* {{Ada/attribute|Fore}} (Ada&nbsp;83 only)
* {{Ada/attribute|Safe_Emax}} (Ada&nbsp;83 only)
* {{Ada/attribute|Safe_Large}} (Ada&nbsp;83 only)
* {{Ada/attribute|Safe_Small}} (Ada&nbsp;83 only)
* {{Ada/attribute|Width}} (Ada&nbsp;83 only)

